substitution_rules
  id program_plan_rules
  rule path_argument_list_files
    order 10
    event manual
    when codepoints 114 101 113 117 101 115 116 58 109 111 100 105 102 105 101 114 32 45 62 32 112 97 116 104 95 97 114 103 117 109 101 110 116
    replace codepoints 114 101 113 117 101 115 116 58 116 97 115 107 32 45 62 32 108 105 115 116 95 102 105 108 101 115
      with codepoints 114 101 113 117 101 115 116 58 116 97 115 107 32 45 62 32 108 105 115 116 95 102 105 108 101 115 95 97 114 103
  rule path_argument_list_files_reverse_sort
    order 10
    event manual
    when codepoints 114 101 113 117 101 115 116 58 109 111 100 105 102 105 101 114 32 45 62 32 112 97 116 104 95 97 114 103 117 109 101 110 116
    replace codepoints 114 101 113 117 101 115 116 58 116 97 115 107 32 45 62 32 108 105 115 116 95 102 105 108 101 115 95 114 101 118 101 114 115 101 95 115 111 114 116
      with codepoints 114 101 113 117 101 115 116 58 116 97 115 107 32 45 62 32 108 105 115 116 95 102 105 108 101 115 95 97 114 103 95 114 101 118 101 114 115 101 95 115 111 114 116
  rule reverse_sort_list_files
    order 20
    event manual
    when codepoints 114 101 113 117 101 115 116 58 109 111 100 105 102 105 101 114 32 45 62 32 114 101 118 101 114 115 101 95 115 111 114 116
    replace codepoints 114 101 113 117 101 115 116 58 116 97 115 107 32 45 62 32 108 105 115 116 95 102 105 108 101 115
      with codepoints 114 101 113 117 101 115 116 58 116 97 115 107 32 45 62 32 108 105 115 116 95 102 105 108 101 115 95 114 101 118 101 114 115 101 95 115 111 114 116
  rule reverse_sort_list_files_arg
    order 20
    event manual
    when codepoints 114 101 113 117 101 115 116 58 109 111 100 105 102 105 101 114 32 45 62 32 114 101 118 101 114 115 101 95 115 111 114 116
    replace codepoints 114 101 113 117 101 115 116 58 116 97 115 107 32 45 62 32 108 105 115 116 95 102 105 108 101 115 95 97 114 103
      with codepoints 114 101 113 117 101 115 116 58 116 97 115 107 32 45 62 32 108 105 115 116 95 102 105 108 101 115 95 97 114 103 95 114 101 118 101 114 115 101 95 115 111 114 116
